WEBVTT

00:00:05.504 --> 00:00:07.398
Bolalik davrimizda biz hammasidan ham

00:00:07.398 --> 00:00:10.959
yadroviy urush boshlanishidan
qo'rqar edik.

00:00:11.819 --> 00:00:15.085
Shu sabab hammaning yerto'lasida
suv va konservalar

00:00:15.085 --> 00:00:17.656
to'ldirilgan bochkalar bo'lar edi.

00:00:18.256 --> 00:00:19.901
Yadroviy urush boshlangan taqdirda

00:00:19.901 --> 00:00:24.637
pastga tushib, o'sha yerda o'tirib, 
bochkadagi zahiradan oziqlanishimiz uchun.

00:00:25.877 --> 00:00:29.597
Hozirgi kunda eng katta global falokat

00:00:29.597 --> 00:00:32.457
bunday ko'rinishda emas.